#

Grilled Chicken with Garlic and Lemon

30 min
$12.99
350 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Dietary Tags:

high-proteingluten-freelow-carb

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main Course

Tags:

chickengrillingeasyhealthy

Description

Juicy grilled chicken marinated in a zesty garlic and lemon mix, perfect for a quick, flavorful meal.

Ingredients

  • chicken breasts: 4 pieces
  • garlic: 4 cloves
  • lemon juice: 1/4 cup
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: 1 teaspoon
  • black pepper: 1/2 teaspoon
  • fresh parsley: for garnish
